Full-stack Team Lead
At Wanna, we build engaging and interactive fashion experiences to serve the next generation of fashion e-commerce. With our signature shoes and watches Virtual Try-Ons, we work for great customers like Gucci, Louis Vuitton, Dolce&Gabbana, IWC, GOAT, Massimo Dutti, and many more. Our products employ proprietary state-of-the-art computer vision, deep learning, and physically-based rendering technologies. For more information, please visit www.wanna.fashion.

