‚óè Excellent communication skills.
Bonus points:
‚óè Experience with WASM, WebGPU & WebGL;
‚óè Experience with neural network inference in Web.
Life with WANNA:
‚óè You will learn a lot about 3D and augmented reality technologies and will be at the forefront of the new industry-shaping trend;
‚óè You‚Äôll work on a unique product that combines different ends of the technological spectrum (AI, computer vision, 3D graphics, Web/Native development, scalable infrastructure);
‚óè Extremely talented and recognized team of world-class professionals;
